text: Gangleri may refer to: * one of Odin's many nicknames meaning "the wanderer" or "Wayweary" * the name of the ancient Swedish king Gylfi, given while in disguise, as described in the book Gylfaginning collected in the Prose Edda * the name of the Icelandic magazine Gangleri, t√≠marit, an organ of the Theosophical Society in Iceland.
title: Gangleri
